      "message": "[Critical] Line 51: 🔴 Critical Issues: The registry is never wired into `SocketPair`, so `getOrCreate(callId, streamType)` in tests creates simulators that are not attached to any media stream. The README advertises this as the way to attach simulators, but no production/test path looks up the registry and calls `SocketPair::setNetworkSimulator()`. Add an integration point during RTP session/socket setup, or remove the registry/docs until it is actually connected.\n\n```suggestion\nauto sim \u003d NetworkSimRegistry::instance().get(callId, streamType);\nif (sim)\n    socketPair_-\u003esetNetworkSimulator(sim);\n```",
